# Agent layer overrides (Layer 3)
# Variables here OVERRIDE common.env values specifically for deployed agent containers.
# Deployed agents run inside DinD and may need different addresses than SAM runtime.
#
# Most variables come from common.env. Only add overrides here if agents
# need different values than the SAM runtime container.
#
# The bootstrap script handles address translation automatically:
# - SAM runtime uses SOLACE_BROKER_URL and S3_ENDPOINT_URL from overrides/<env>.env
# - Agent containers use AGENT_BROKER_URL and AGENT_S3_ENDPOINT_URL from overrides/<env>.env
#
# Add any agent-specific overrides below:
